  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if SAF312 eye drops have an adequate safety and
      efficacy profile to justify further clinical development for the treatment of ocular pain
      associated with corneal epithelial defect such as after photorefractive keratectomy (PRK)
      surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
